  <brief_title>Apremilast in the Treatment of Uveitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label Trial to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Apremilast in the Management of Vision-threatening Uveitis That is Refractory to Other Modes of Systemic Immunosuppression.</official_title>
